column16: Josh Reddick singles on a ground ball to center fielder Ezequiel Carrera.
Alex Bregman homers (13) on a fly ball to right center field.    Tyler White scores.
Derek Fisher grounds out softly, second baseman Rob Refsnyder to first baseman Justin Smoak.   Brian McCann scores.    Tyler White to 3rd.
Ben Revere grounds out, first baseman Justin Smoak to pitcher Matt Dermody.
Luis Valbuena out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Ezequiel Carrera.   Shane Robinson scores.
Andrelton Simmons pops out to first baseman Justin Smoak in foul territory.
Shane Robinson singles on a ground ball to shortstop Ryan Goins, deflected by third baseman Russell Martin.
Albert Pujols grounds into a double play, third baseman Russell Martin to second baseman Rob Refsnyder to first baseman Justin Smoak.   Mike Trout out at 2nd.
Yunel Escobar lines out to center fielder Kevin Pillar.
Kaleb Cowart grounds into a double play, shortstop Ryan Goins to second baseman Rob Refsnyder to first baseman Justin Smoak.   Martin Maldonado out at 2nd.
Ben Revere grounds out, shortstop Ryan Goins to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Kole Calhoun singles on a ground ball to center fielder Kevin Pillar.   Andrelton Simmons scores.
Manny Machado homers (2) on a fly ball to right field.    Adam Jones scores.
Craig Gentry homers (1) on a fly ball to left field.   Jonathan Schoop scores.
J.   Hardy pops out to first baseman Kendrys Morales in foul territory.
Jonathan Schoop singles on a fly ball to right fielder Ezequiel Carrera.
Trey Mancini homers (4) on a fly ball to center field.
